{"tid":1838453,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"X1解散粉絲靜坐求重組","createTime":"2020-01-24T04:32:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T04:40:18.000Z","uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"706765cae64d9f1a1243ae180f523061691dcc94","tid":1838453,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:32:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3582373/org/22c4337cbe33d15a0bc5dd8435840103.jpg/aZtQNowdo7gl3k5bbrLyIYiDYybZaxq0LZqtAC2arQA?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3582373%2Forg%2F22c4337cbe33d15a0bc5dd8435840103.jpg%2FaZtQNowdo7gl3k5bbrLyIYiDYybZaxq0LZqtAC2arQA%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=e39ff410&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n韓國Mnet電視台人氣選秀節目《Produce X 101》出身的限定男團X1，因製作人安俊英被爆造假及受賄，組合去年11月開始停工。雖然製作公司CJ ENM承諾會為造假風波負責，全力支援X1復工，組合卻於本月6日解散收場，引起粉絲不滿！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n昨日，近千粉絲在CJ ENM大樓外靜坐抗議，由代表讀出聲明書，批評製作公司不負責任，要求有關方面為有意重組的成員組織新男團，履行向X1成員作出補償的承諾，亦有逾4,000名海外粉絲簽名支持X1重組。製作公司表示對X1解散感到十分可惜，將繼續支援成員的活動，但被粉絲批評「得個講字」，要求他們對重組X1作出正面回應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3895209/org/61b5db2c06df7eea6fccd9abafb429aa.jpg/oiKzvC--cqduFr7aNazYeKZOVLTWQ1aU49iGBOPYhgQ?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3895209%2Forg%2F61b5db2c06df7eea6fccd9abafb429aa.jpg%2FoiKzvC--cqduFr7aNazYeKZOVLTWQ1aU49iGBOPYhgQ%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=f7e8a708&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1dae941ad8b1d9214c4b84a235c40d5fef152cb3","tid":1838453,"uid":5055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:40:18.000Z","msg":"不了"}]}